world discovered

00:02:36.700 --> 00:02:39.010 align:middle line:84%
that the greed of
a handful of people

00:02:39.010 --> 00:02:43.000 align:middle line:84%
was jeopardizing the future
of the entire planet.

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:44.620 align:middle line:84%
I was now convinced
that the system

00:02:44.620 --> 00:02:47.620 align:middle line:84%
was incapable of providing
a solution to the problems

00:02:47.620 --> 00:02:49.560 align:middle line:90%
that it had created.

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:51.720 align:middle line:84%
And as a water
salesman in Manhattan,

00:02:51.720 --> 00:02:53.770 align:middle line:90%
I was also part of the problem.

00:02:53.770 --> 00:02:56.760 align:middle line:90%
But what could I do about it?

00:02:56.760 --> 00:03:00.600 align:middle line:84%
I was afraid I might turn into
a cynic or fall into depression.

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:03.330 align:middle line:84%
So I decided to leave
everything behind

00:03:03.330 --> 00:03:06.450 align:middle line:84%
and go search for the
answers to my questions.

00:03:06.450 --> 00:03:09.562 align:middle line:84%
I had no clue of what
I was getting into.

00:03:09.562 --> 00:03:13.498 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:03:13.498 --> 00:03:29.760 align:middle line:90%


00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:32.010 align:middle line:84%
>> At that time, I
was presenting my film

00:03:32.010 --> 00:03:35.050 align:middle line:90%
in a festival in New Delhi.

00:03:35.050 --> 00:03:37.720 align:middle line:84%
Marc just showed
up out of the blue.

00:03:37.720 --> 00:03:40.450 align:middle line:84%
