him for a while,

00:03:45.387 --> 00:03:47.220 align:middle line:84%
I thought it might be
interesting to capture

00:03:47.220 --> 00:03:49.290 align:middle line:84%
his personality
and his eagerness

00:03:49.290 --> 00:03:51.327 align:middle line:84%
