>> [NON-ENGLISH]

00:06:58.150 --> 00:07:02.190 align:middle line:90%


00:07:02.190 --> 00:07:04.450 align:middle line:84%
>> After our visit
with Prima and Anand,

00:07:04.450 --> 00:07:06.610 align:middle line:84%
