several irresponsible global

00:07:17.710 --> 00:07:20.110 align:middle line:84%
corporations sentenced
at the International

00:07:20.110 --> 00:07:21.430 align:middle line:90%
Court of the Hague.

00:07:21.430 --> 00:07:23.620 align:middle line:84%
I had seen her in
Nathanael's documentaries

00:07:23.620 --> 00:07:25.330 align:middle line:90%
