00:07:35.320 --> 00:07:39.160 align:middle line:84%
And the fresh air of thinking
fresh is the value of Gandhi.

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:41.410 align:middle line:84%
I mean, besides
what he did for us

00:07:41.410 --> 00:07:43.420 align:middle line:84%
as a country in the
independence movement,

00:07:43.420 --> 00:07:46.020 align:middle line:90%
but globally today, you know?

00:07:46.020 --> 00:07:48.530 align:middle line:90%
He allows us to think fresh.

00:07:48.530 --> 00:07:52.410 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:07:52.410 --> 00:07:57.745 align:middle line:90%


