00:08:56.930 --> 00:09:01.550 align:middle line:84%
And sitting in privileged
jobs, isolated from society,

00:09:01.550 --> 00:09:04.160 align:middle line:84%
you could keep making
excuses, but you

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:05.450 align:middle line:90%
wouldn't bring the change.

00:09:05.450 --> 00:09:08.060 align:middle line:84%
So I threw up my
job, came back home,

00:09:08.060 --> 00:09:10.460 align:middle line:84%
started to work from
my mother's cowshed,

00:09:10.460 --> 00:09:12.740 align:middle line:84%
and that's what I've
been doing since then.

00:09:12.740 --> 00:09:19.730 align:middle line:90%


00:09:19.730 --> 00:09:21.230 align:middle line:84%
So things are
changing, but they are

00:09:21.230 --> 00:09:24.770 align:middle line:84%
changing in the wrong direction,
