00:09:24.770 --> 00:09:27.890 align:middle line:84%
driven by giant corporations
who are turning everything

00:09:27.890 --> 00:09:30.652 align:middle line:84%
into a market and turning
everything into a commodity.

00:09:30.652 --> 00:09:33.110 align:middle line:84%
There are no people, there's
no nature, there's no culture,

00:09:33.110 --> 00:09:33.910 align:middle line:90%
there's no value.

00:09:33.910 --> 00:09:37.990 align:middle line:90%


00:09:37.990 --> 00:09:41.090 align:middle line:84%
