is a change that

00:09:41.090 --> 00:09:44.360 align:middle line:84%
helps us recognize
that if we continue

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:48.380 align:middle line:84%
in this present path
of change, humanity

00:09:48.380 --> 00:09:51.200 align:middle line:84%
will annihilate the conditions
for its living on this planet.

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:55.310 align:middle line:90%


00:09:55.310 --> 00:09:57.740 align:middle line:84%
Climate change is one
of those dimensions.

00:09:57.740 --> 00:10:00.045 align:middle line:84%
Disappearance of food
is another dimension.

00:10:00.045 --> 00:10:02.420 align:middle line:84%
