00:10:07.790 --> 00:10:08.480 align:middle line:90%
gone?

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:10.070 align:middle line:84%
They don't know how
they'll do that.

00:10:10.070 --> 00:10:13.730 align:middle line:90%


00:10:13.730 --> 00:10:16.550 align:middle line:84%
So the recognition
that nature is

00:10:16.550 --> 00:10:19.950 align:middle line:84%
the condition of our being alive
is the shift we have to make.

00:10:19.950 --> 00:10:22.340 align:middle line:84%
We have to stop thinking
of nature as wilderness

00:10:22.340 --> 00:10:24.660 align:middle line:84%
and start thinking of it
as a condition for life.

00:10:24.660 --> 00:10:31.870 align:middle line:90%
[WILDLIFE SOUNDS]

00:10:31.870 --> 00:10:35.830 align:middle line:84%
>> Where do people begin to
