a pot in your backyard.

00:10:59.960 --> 00:11:02.000 align:middle line:90%
A little kitchen garden.

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:04.330 align:middle line:84%
A link with a farmer
in your neighborhood.

00:11:04.330 --> 00:11:07.020 align:middle line:84%
