Spend a lot of time.

00:26:03.338 --> 00:26:44.240 align:middle line:90%


00:26:44.240 --> 00:26:47.680 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:26:47.680 --> 00:26:53.990 align:middle line:90%


00:26:53.990 --> 00:26:57.370 align:middle line:84%
>> Once we returned to France,
