00:31:38.010 --> 00:31:39.290 align:middle line:90%
Lenoir.

00:31:39.290 --> 00:31:41.960 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:31:41.960 --> 00:34:08.949 align:middle line:90%


00:34:08.949 --> 00:34:12.070 align:middle line:84%
>> At that point, my goal was
not so much to reconnect with

00:34:12.070 --> 00:34:15.443 align:middle line:84%
