00:34:15.443 --> 00:34:17.110 align:middle line:84%
the workplace and the
world of business.

00:34:17.110 --> 00:34:26.870 align:middle line:90%


00:34:26.870 --> 00:34:30.690 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:34:30.690 --> 00:34:39.840 align:middle line:90%


00:34:39.840 --> 00:34:42.600 align:middle line:84%
>> My old employer was offering
