00:43:07.310 --> 00:43:15.950 align:middle line:90%


00:43:15.950 --> 00:43:19.095 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:43:19.095 --> 00:43:56.470 align:middle line:90%


00:43:56.470 --> 00:44:00.740 align:middle line:84%
>> After our stay in Chapas,
