00:48:36.300 --> 00:48:39.310 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:48:39.310 --> 00:49:42.268 align:middle line:90%


00:49:42.268 --> 00:49:47.238 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:49:47.238 --> 00:50:05.460 align:middle line:90%


00:50:05.460 --> 00:50:07.770 align:middle line:84%
>> Having just arrived
