00:50:10.560 --> 00:50:13.650 align:middle line:90%


00:50:13.650 --> 00:50:15.510 align:middle line:84%
Our rational way
of thinking needed

00:50:15.510 --> 00:50:18.450 align:middle line:84%
to confront the teachings
