00:50:26.780 --> 00:50:28.415 align:middle line:90%
and ask him a few questions.

00:50:28.415 --> 00:50:39.570 align:middle line:90%


00:50:39.570 --> 00:50:43.050 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:50:43.050 --> 00:52:54.500 align:middle line:90%


00:52:54.500 --> 00:52:57.850 align:middle line:84%
