00:54:46.450 --> 00:54:51.490 align:middle line:84%
And so one of the things that
self inquiry brings to us,

00:54:51.490 --> 00:54:54.450 align:middle line:84%
one of the things that
contemplative practices can

00:54:54.450 --> 00:54:59.280 align:middle line:84%
