recognize that our thoughts are

00:54:59.280 --> 00:55:00.960 align:middle line:90%
just thoughts.

00:55:00.960 --> 00:55:03.720 align:middle line:84%
Our beliefs are
just our beliefs.

00:55:03.720 --> 00:55:06.690 align:middle line:84%
And they are not
really who we are.

00:55:06.690 --> 00:55:09.750 align:middle line:84%
They're just sort of
working hypotheses.

00:55:09.750 --> 00:55:16.580 align:middle line:90%


00:55:16.580 --> 00:55:19.630 align:middle line:84%
So you may be, for example,
sitting in meditation

00:55:19.630 --> 00:55:24.910 align:middle line:84%
