00:55:30.370 --> 00:55:34.150 align:middle line:84%
What if I didn't see the
world as a dangerous place?

00:55:34.150 --> 00:55:37.270 align:middle line:84%
And when that kind
of a shift happens,

00:55:37.270 --> 00:55:42.880 align:middle line:84%
