change, relationships change,

00:55:42.880 --> 00:55:46.610 align:middle line:84%
motivations, priorities,
values change.

00:55:46.610 --> 00:55:48.730 align:middle line:84%
And that's really the
kind of transformation

00:55:48.730 --> 00:55:50.200 align:middle line:90%
we are interested in studying.

