00:58:00.650 --> 00:58:03.100 align:middle line:84%
we have to change
the belief systems.

00:58:03.100 --> 00:58:05.200 align:middle line:84%
Einstein's-- I love
the famous quote.

00:58:05.200 --> 00:58:09.550 align:middle line:84%
It's like, you cannot solve the
