How did we get here?

00:58:25.190 --> 00:58:28.350 align:middle line:90%


00:58:28.350 --> 00:58:31.520 align:middle line:90%
Why are we here?

00:58:31.520 --> 00:58:33.300 align:middle line:84%
And how do we make
