have a spiritual element.

00:59:04.310 --> 00:59:05.630 align:middle line:90%
It's just the physical world.

00:59:05.630 --> 00:59:06.470 align:middle line:90%
It's like a clock.

00:59:06.470 --> 00:59:07.270 align:middle line:90%
It's a machine.

00:59:07.270 --> 00:59:10.610 align:middle line:90%


00:59:10.610 --> 00:59:13.660 align:middle line:84%
So when science
